Question 4 – Grade Classification (Nested if-else)
Scenario:
80 and above : Grade A
60–79       : Grade B
50–59       : Grade C
Below 50    : Fail

#answer
user_score = input("Enter your score: ")
score = int(user_score)

if score >= 80:
    print("Grade A")
elif score >= 60:
    print("Grade B")
elif score >= 50:
    print("Grade C")
else:
    print("Fail")
